Based off Richards.D's DAR_MTVR mod.
https://forums.bohemia.net/forums/topic/167577-a3-medium-tactical-vehicle-replacement-mtvr-mod-release/


This is a mod for Arma 3 adding a few MTVR variants. Features include switching between passenger and cargo modes, player-stowable cargo covers, heavy Vehicle in Vehicle support, and blackout lights.

Released under the Arma Public License
https://www.bistudio.com/community/licenses/arma-public-license
